### Try to get current user (should fail, not authorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Try to get current user (should succeed, authorized via cookies)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Refresh token (should succeed, rotates cookies)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh

### Try to get current user (should succeed, authorized with new cookies)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Logout (should succeed, clears cookies)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout

### Try to get current user (should fail, cookies cleared)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Try to refresh token (should fail, cookies cleared)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
